Trivia #86: Maribel Hearn's exact name has never been made clear by ZUN. This is due to her name being written as "Maeriberii Haan" and has never been romanized in any official work. Maribel is a very rough translation of Maeriberii, and Hearn comes from Lafcadio Hearn, a man who served as inspiration for Maribel and Yukari. ZUN himself has stated that he's unsure of how to spell her name.
